<p><strong><em>Note</em></strong>: The maximum length of the item name is 240 characters.
The item name is used to create the item URL.
Open the plentyShop LTS assistant and navigate to the step SEO if you want to decide whether name 1, 2 or 3 should be used for the meta title and the item URL.</p>
