<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Enter an item text.
The item text is a detailed description, which is displayed in the item layout in the plentyShop.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Note</em></strong>: Click on the drop-down list in the upper right corner and select your preferred editor for entering text or HTML.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Technical data</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Enter technical data for the item.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Note</em></strong>: Click on the drop-down list in the upper right corner and select your preferred editor for entering text or HTML.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
