The name is relevant for SEO, i.e. it helps search engines index the item.
Use appropriate keywords in the image names to make the images more relevant to search engines.
This also increases traffic on the page, for example if the image is found with the Google image search.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Note</em></strong>:
The image name is limited to 256 characters.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
