<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The file formats supported for images are: PNG, JPG, GIF, SVG</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>File names</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Image file names may contain the following characters:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>Letters (a-z, A-Z) excluding umlauts</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Numbers (0-9)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Underscores (_)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Hyphens (-)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Spaces and special characters such as umlauts are not permitted. When you upload images, spaces and special characters are replaced by hyphens (-).</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
