<p>Every time an item image is uploaded, plentymarkets creates the following versions:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>High-resolution item image</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Medium-sized item image</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Item attribute image</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Two preview images</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Since plentymarkets does not scale up images, the source image must have at least the size and quality specified in the <a href="/en/item/settings/images#500">Sizes</a> area. Larger images will be scaled down to the specified size.</p>
</div></div></td>
