<p>Go to <strong>CMS » Web design</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open a template in the <strong>Layout » ItemView</strong> folder.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Insert the code example into the template.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> (<span class="icon green"><i class="psicon-save"></i></span>) the settings.<br>
