The value is used to calculate shipping packages and weight-based shipping costs.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Item bundles</em></strong>: The gross weight can <a href="/en/item/use-cases/combining-products#2500">automatically be calculated based on the bundle components</a>.</p>
