<p><strong><em>Background info</em></strong>: The net weight is the weight of the variation without packaging.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Item bundles</em></strong>: The net weight can <a href="/en/item/use-cases/combining-products#2500">automatically be calculated based on the bundle components</a>.</p>
