<p>Select this option (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-check-square  "></i></span>) if you want the unit price to be displayed in the plentyShop.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Background info</em></strong>:
The unit price tells you how much the item costs per pound, litre or other unit of measure.
It’s calculated based on the item’s <a href="/en/item/settings/units">unit</a>, <a href="/en/item/managing-items#intable-content">content</a> and <a href="/en/item/managing-items#240">price</a>.
