</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Note</em></strong>: The purchase price is either <a href="/en/stock-management/new-incoming-items#300">calculated automatically or managed manually</a> depending on how the settings were saved in the menu <strong>Setup » Stock » Stock » Incoming items</strong>.</p>
