</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Note</em></strong>: In plentymarkets, it’s possible to save a different customs tariff number for each variation.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong><em>Example</em></strong>: In some countries, children’s clothing is taxed differently depending on the size.
