<p><a href="/en/item/import-export-create/create/new-item">While creating the variation</a>, you already specified which category the variation should be sorted into.
Here in this tab, you can <em>link additional categories</em> to the variation.
The variation will be displayed in all of the selected categories in the plentyShop.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Linking additional categories:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Item » Edit item</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="/en/item/introduction/search#400">Search for</a> and open the variation.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>Categories</strong> tab in the lower row.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-plus  "></i></span> <strong>Link category</strong>.<br>
→ The <strong>Link category</strong> window opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the appropriate category or sub-category.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-plus  "></i></span> <strong>Link category</strong>.<br>
→ The category is linked and displayed in the <strong>Linked categories</strong> area.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock tip">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-tip" title="Tip"></i>
</td>
