However, you can deactivate the <a href="/en/item/introduction/inheritance">inheritance function</a> if you want to configure differing settings for a sub-variation.</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Open the sub-variation and click on the tab <strong>Categories</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Deactivate inheritance</strong> (<span class="icon "><i class="psicon-item_variation_inheritance"></i></span>).</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Configure the category settings for the sub-variation.</p>
</li>
<li>
